cafe

Class Donut

  • java.lang.Object
    • cafe.MenuItem
      • cafe.Donut

  • public class Donut
extends MenuItem
    An instance of this class is a menu item in an order. This class must extend MenuItem class. The Donut class handles the donutType, donutFalvor and quantity that the user chooses. It also performs the calculation of the donuts the user has ordered.
    Author:
    Prachiti Atigre, Ujani Patel
